tesla-tsla-stock-a-golden-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 20:30:00"}, {"id": "4743641", "title": "Another 50bp Bank Of Canada Cut, But Smaller Moves Lie Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up of Canadian banknotes (CAD) background\" data-id=\"846636558\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MJ_Prototype</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/james-knightley/\" rel=\"nofollow\">James Knightley</a></em></p> <h2><span>Growing economic slack prompts a second consecutive 50bp rate cut</span></h2> <p>Bank of Canada has cut its policy interest rate 50bp to 3.25%, as expected. Last week's surprise jump in unemployment to 6.8% from 6.5% helped cement the call, but inflation</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/846636558/image_846636558.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743641-another-50bp-bank-of-canada-cut-smaller-moves-lie-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 20:25:00"}, {"id": "4743627", "title": "Immunome: A Recently Acquired Lead Asset And A Small Market", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"House on the edge\" data-id=\"1445810160\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1047px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Immunome (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IMNM\" title=\"Immunome, Inc.\">IMNM</a></span>) is a late stage developer of cancer therapies. Its lead asset is AL102, a gamma secretase inhibitor in a Phase 3 trial for the treatment of desmoid tumor. All other assets are preclinical.</p> <h2>Background</h2> <p>Immunome has a turbulent</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810160/image_1445810160.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743627-immunome-a-recently-acquired-lead-asset-and-a-small-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 20:20:22"}, {"id": "4743624", "title": "NexGen Energy's Offtake Agreement: A De-Risking Event, A Confirmation Of The Uranium Bull Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Uranium, a chemical element with a U symbol and an atomic mass equal to 238 u, has an atomic number 92\" data-id=\"1304747275\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">RHJ</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>What</h2> <p>On December 4, 2024, <em>NexGen Energy Ltd</em>. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NXE\" title=\"NexGen Energy Ltd.\">NXE</a></span>) <a href=\"https://www.nexgenenergy.ca/news/news-details/2024/NexGen-Announces-First-Uranium-Sales-Contracts-for-5-Million-Pounds-with-Major-US-Utilities/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">announced</a> its first uranium sales agreements, signed with multiple U.S. utilities, to supply 1 Mlb per year of U3O8 from 2029 to 2033 from its flagship Rook I project in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304747275/image_1304747275.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743624-nexgen-energy-offtake-agreement-de-risking-event-confirms-uranium-bull-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 20:14:53"}]}